Pokud se jedn o podezelho,
tak by to znamenalo ztratit stopu.

218
00:25:20,840 --> 00:25:24,594
Dstojnice s vaimi zkuenostmi
by mla vdt, co znamen "nechat to plynout".

219
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:28,076
