Tolerovala byste to sam, co my?

225
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:49,511
Wong Kar Ling, tm svm vslechem
na inspektorku Kao dor.

226
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:52,438
J si nemyslm, e by se chovala zlomysln.

227
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:57,588
Tenhle ppad je dleit.
Nepovedu tm, co mn nerespektuje.

228
00:25:57,720 --> 00:26:00,632
Mla bych ten ppad pedat inspektoru Wongovi.

229
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:05,237
Spoluprce vytv lep vsledek.

230
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:07,920
Tento ppad byste mli mt
na starosti vy oba.

231
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:10,713
Te u s tm problm nem, Wong Kar Ling?

232
00:26:10,840 --> 00:26:11,989
Ne.

233
00:26:13,080 --> 00:26:15,196
Jak mohou operaci vst 2 lidi?

234
00:26:15,320 --> 00:26:18,232
Komu mm hlsit,
pokud se nco stane?

235
00:26:18,360 --> 00:26:21,352
