jen za ruku, ne za prsa.

256
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:54,916
Sleno, vy jste chytr?

257
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:59,477
Tm, e ji budu dret za ruku
a na vs koukat, doshnu toho samho.

258
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:06,158
- Pro si na sebe neahte sm?!
- Jak si peje.

259
00:28:06,280 --> 00:28:08,874
Mikeu, pojme se ped nima oahvat.

260
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:11,992
Budem se oahvat, fe.

261
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:21,876
Kdy mte rd osahvn, pane,
co mi takhle zaplatil pesas?

262
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,797
Jak rd tohle slym.

263
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:27,799
fe, vemte si njak tablety,
