00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:20,149
- Mazej.
- Nesmme nae utajen prozradit.

284
00:30:20,280 --> 00:30:23,556
- Policistka. To jsou vci.
- Co se stalo, pane?

285
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:28,151
