00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:42,558
- Rozumm, konec.
- Ano.

300
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,669
Ano.

301
00:31:44,280 --> 00:31:47,317
Dlej, co km a zarum,
e bude v podku.

302
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:52,392
Dlej, co km j a nic
se ti nestane. Poj se mnou.

303
00:31:52,520 --> 00:31:55,239
M nic nen a nepotebuju,
abys mi to zaruovala.

304
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:06,638
Potm je to dokonce zbavnj.

305
00:32:12,880 --> 00:32:15,189
Rozsvtme a mrknem na kozy.

306
00:32:20,760 --> 00:32:21,988
Loupe!

307
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:41,994
Pojme dovnit.

308
00:32:55,600 --> 00:32:56,919
Dol!

309
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:14,749
Pry.

310
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:33,392
Tudy.

311
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:38,914
Policie. Zptky.

