Ne!

315
00:34:15,720 --> 00:34:18,632
- Jdte beze mn.
- Jdeme!

316
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:38,393
Chytej!

317
00:34:43,560 --> 00:34:45,516
Uhnte!

318
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:02,876
Uhnte!

319
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:36,317
Doshneme na pomsty.

320
00:35:39,240 --> 00:35:43,119
Vte, jak je rozdl mezi tmito
tymi zprvami a tou va?

321
00:35:43,240 --> 00:35:46,118
- Ani ne.
- Ani ne? J vm to povm.

322
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:50,756
Mte na tom osobn zjem.
Kryjete svou vagrovou.

323
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:54,429
Tenhle ppad ztroskotal,
protoe je prchliv

324
