350
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:43,997
Nebu takov, Ling.

351
00:37:44,120 --> 00:37:46,236
Pestate se prt.

352
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:49,113
Pestate. Nechte toho.

353
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:53,919
Promite, mete jt ven?
