00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:42,751
Podvej se, kdo tu je.
Nechej toho.

375
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:45,474
Pestate tu okount.
Vrate se do prce.

376
00:39:45,600 --> 00:39:47,158
Nepla.

377
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:04,030
Tum, vezmi si ho.

378
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:11,400
Matka m dnes narozeniny.
Nepla.

379
00:40:11,520 --> 00:40:13,511
Odejdi brzy a pevle se.

380
00:40:13,640 --> 00:40:16,359
Ty se piprav.
Zaruuju ti, e t opiju.

381
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:20,350
Matka m dnes narozeniny.
Promluvme si o tom jindy.

382
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:22,471
Pesta plakat, ano?

383
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,992
Pro matku.

384
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:34,236
