k narozeninm nejdv zazpvat?

422
00:47:13,080 --> 00:47:14,718
Ano.

423
00:47:44,680 --> 00:47:47,035
Mino!

424
00:47:47,160 --> 00:47:49,310
Jsi v podku?

425
00:47:51,440 --> 00:47:54,000
Je mi fajn.

426
00:47:54,560 --> 00:47:59,315
Matce o Chung Boovi nekej.

427
00:47:59,440 --> 00:48:01,158
J vm.

428
00:48:03,760 --> 00:48:05,910
Pojme za nimi.

429
00:48:23,880 --> 00:48:27,759
- Podvejte, pila Mina a Ling.
- Jdou opravdu pozd.

430
00:48:28,680 --> 00:48:31,148
No tak,
pipnte si tyhle broe.

431
00:48:31,640 --> 00:48:36,316
- Pro jdete tak pozd, lidi?
- Kde jste, vy dv, byly?

432
00:48:37,400 --> 00:48:42,110
Chtli jsme na vs pokat,
ale editel ns popohnl.

433
00:48:42,240 --> 00:48:43,992
Pojme zptky.

434
00:48:44,120 --> 00:48:46,918
- Matko!.
- Opozdilci.

435
00:48:47,040 --> 00:48:51,238
Posa se. Mina a Ling
ti pili poblahopt.

436
00:48:51,360 --> 00:48:53,749
eknte nco.

437
00:48:55,440 --> 00:48:58,830
Pejeme matce dlouh ivot
a hodn tst.

438
00:48:58,960 --> 00:49:00,951
A aby se ti splnila vechna pn.

439
00:49:01,080 --> 00:49:03,958
Dobe.
Tady je nco na pilepenou.

440
00:49:04,080 --> 00:49:06,913
Matka je dnes veer moc astn.

441
00:49:07,040 --> 00:49:08,234
Nejdv vsta.

442
00:49:11,280 --> 00:49:13,157
Hele, pestate.

443
00:49:13,280 --> 00:49:16,909
Ty jsi zaujat, matko.
Podvme se my.

444
00:49:17,040 --> 00:49:18,678
"Zlat chvoj a nefritov lstky"?

445
00:49:18,800 --> 00:49:23,396
To znamen hodn tst pro ni,
ale tak hodn potomk pro slenu Wong.

446
00:49:23,520 --> 00:49:26,193
Pli jste si, aby se pn
pan Wong splnila.

447
00:49:26,320 --> 00:49:29,392
Vn douf ve vnouata.

448
00:49:29,520 --> 00:49:33,798
Symbol plodnosti?
Vezmi si to zptky, prosm.

449
00:49:33,920 --> 00:49:37,117
Kde je Bo?
On jet pracuje?

450
00:49:38,280 --> 00:49:41,511
Jdlo stydne.
Pojme zptky ke stolu.

451
00:49:41,640 --> 00:49:43,835
Chung Bo pijde pozdji.
Pojme jst.

452
00:49:43,960 --> 00:49:45,791
Ano, my hladovme.

453
00:49:49,560 --> 00:49:51,437
Pokat, pokat.

454
00:49:52,920 --> 00:49:56,151
Matko, tady je tvj oblben  -
sele jazek.

455
00:49:58,120 --> 00:50:02,955
Kdy tu Bo nen, tak se s tebou
o tu sele noku prt nebude.

456
00:50:03,080 --> 00:50:08,313
Co? Vdycky se o ni s Boem pere.
Co se to s tebou dje?

457
00:50:12,800 --> 00:50:15,473
- J si ji vezmu.
- Pesta pedstrat, e jsi hodn.

458
00:50:20,760 --> 00:50:23,433
J ji potrestm za tebe, matko.

459
00:50:23,560 --> 00:50:26,154
Dvej si pozor na pusu.

460
00:50:26,280 --> 00:50:29,556
Schovej tu noku pro Boa, Lai.

461
00:50:29,680 --> 00:50:31,398
Ano.

462
00:50:32,000 --> 00:50:35,913
Samozejm,
je to jedin syn v rodin.

463
00:50:36,920 --> 00:50:39,673
Podala bys mi talek, Mino?

464
00:51:02,280 --> 00:51:06,114
- Bylo dnes v kanceli runo?
- Ne.

465
00:51:06,240 --> 00:51:09,550
Opravdu?
Pro jste pily tak pozd?

466
00:51:11,400 --> 00:51:16,793
Cel den hldme, aby nedochzelo
ke zloinm, matko.

467
00:51:16,920 --> 00:51:20,151
Je sprvn, e plnte sv povinnosti.

468
00:51:20,280 --> 00:51:24,671
Pro jste nezavolali a nedali mi vdt?
Vy jste na mn zapomnli?

469
00:51:27,280 --> 00:51:30,670
Samozejm, e ne, matko.
Chung Bo chtl, abych ti dala tohle.

470
00:51:30,800 --> 00:51:35,555
Podvme se, co to je.
Je to pkn tk.

471
00:51:35,680 --> 00:51:39,832
Pni, to je asn.
Je to zlat etzek s velkm nefritem.

472
00:51:39,960 --> 00:51:43,589
Uka, matko, j ti ho zapnu.
Ten musel bejt drahej.

473
00:51:43,720 --> 00:51:48,840
A se vdm, utratm penze
mho manela za njak velk drek

474
00:51:48,960 --> 00:51:50,837
Takhle bys pemlet nemla.

475
00:51:50,960 --> 00:51:56,671
Mla bys bt jako Mina a pod
se o svho manela starat.

476
00:51:57,320 --> 00:52:01,836
Pokud najdu tak dobrho manela.
jako je Bo, tak urit budu.

477
00:52:01,960 --> 00:52:04,679
- To bys byla astn ena.
- Je Mina opravdu astn?

478
00:52:04,800 --> 00:52:09,032
- Mina m tst, e mho bratra m.
- Bu zticha.

479
00:52:09,160 --> 00:52:12,994
Co se to s tebou dje?
Pln misi v utajen?

480
00:52:13,120 --> 00:52:15,759
Oslavenkyn, rd bych pipil
na vae zdrav.

481
00:52:15,880 --> 00:52:17,154
Dkuji vm.

482
00:52:21,000 --> 00:52:24,037
Bo jet nedorazil?
Doufal jsem, e ho zastihnu.

483
00:52:24,160 --> 00:52:28,676
Bo tu sice nen, ale Mina ano.
Uka, Mino, j ti naliju.

484
00:52:31,680 --> 00:52:34,638
Bojte se, e
nedokete vypt tolik, co Mina?

485
00:52:34,760 --> 00:52:36,910
Prosm, madam, do toho.

486
00:52:42,880 --> 00:52:45,792
J to vypiju msto Miny, strku Ya.

487
00:52:55,320 --> 00:52:57,390
Vy jste staten.

488
00:52:57,520 --> 00:52:59,875
Musm se na vai statenost napt.

489
00:53:08,600 --> 00:53:13,515
J svou skleniku dopil.
Tady je dal. Jste na ad, madam.

490
00:53:14,240 --> 00:53:17,312
Neboj se ho, Mino.
J ti doliju.

491
00:53:17,440 --> 00:53:20,716
Ano, Mino.
Nemj strach, bude v pohod.

492
00:53:20,840 --> 00:53:23,798
Pij na Boovu poest, Mino.

493
00:53:28,200 --> 00:53:31,749
Tohleto vypiju na
Chung Boovu poest, strku Ya.

494
00:53:39,760 --> 00:53:45,153
Ml bych se stydt za to,jak
neumm pt. Vae dvata jsou skvl.

495
00:53:45,280 --> 00:53:49,398
Dkuji vm. I za to, e jste
se o n v poslednch pr letech staral.

496
00:53:49,520 --> 00:53:55,117
Tm, km jsem, bych nebyl
bez dohledu nebotka Wonga.

497
00:53:55,240 --> 00:53:57,196
Te u vs vechny nechm v klidu.

498
00:53:57,320 --> 00:53:59,629
Peji vm bjen veer, matko.

499
00:54:02,640 --> 00:54:07,316
Jsi v podku, Mino? Nepotebuje
se jt do koupelny oplchnout?

500
00:54:07,440 --> 00:54:12,560
- Pomu ti.
- Posly, jsi v podku?

501
00:54:12,680 --> 00:54:15,592
- Jsi v podku, Ling?
- Jsem.

502
00:54:15,720 --> 00:54:17,870
Pojme se napt.

503
00:54:33,040 --> 00:54:38,876
V parku Wu Gao Tam byl
pozd odpoledne zabit vy dstojnk.

504
00:54:39,000 --> 00:54:43,710
Zemel na etn porann
ivotn dleitch orgn.

505
00:54:44,680 --> 00:54:47,558
Policie podezv gang Vietnamc.

506
00:54:47,680 --> 00:54:51,275
Kohokoli, kdo ono zabit vidl
nebo o nm m njak informace

507
00:54:51,400 --> 00:54:56,520
policie d, aby se okamit pihlsil.

508
00:54:56,640 --> 00:55:01,270
Tento vy dstojnkse jmenoval
Chung Bo. Bylo mu 33 let.

509
00:55:01,400 --> 00:55:04,836
U policejnho sboru byl 8 let.

510
00:55:20,000 --> 00:55:21,558
Matko!

511
00:55:21,680 --> 00:55:26,959
Nepla, Mino. Byl to policista.
Dalo se ekat, e se to stane.

512
00:55:28,560 --> 00:55:33,156
Udlej to pro Chung Boa.
Bu staten.

513
00:55:33,280 --> 00:55:35,589
Pojd zase ven.

514
00:55:36,160 --> 00:55:37,912
Ano, matko.

515
00:55:44,720 --> 00:55:46,676
Nepla.

516
00:56:20,760 --> 00:56:22,716
Matko!

517
00:56:46,480 --> 00:56:47,469
Mino.

518
00:56:54,920 --> 00:56:59,277
Omlouvm se, e dnes veer
nememe bt dobrmi spolenky.

519
00:56:59,400 --> 00:57:04,349
Tuto skleniku pozvedm za matku
a vm vem dkuji za pochopen.

520
00:57:11,400 --> 00:57:16,633
Je tk uvit, e datem tv smrti
jsou narozeniny t, kter t porodila

521
00:57:18,360 --> 00:57:21,955
Matka se napije za tebe.

522
00:57:23,160 --> 00:57:28,109
ehnej nm vem z nebe, Bo.

523
00:58:35,800 --> 00:58:39,839
Pro mlad lid umraj?!

524
00:59:35,080 --> 00:59:36,399
BRZY PIJDE DAL.

525
00:59:39,400 --> 00:59:41,072
Pozor, bomba!

526
00:59:47,560 --> 00:59:48,993
Mino!

527
01:00:10,920 --> 01:00:14,390
- U jde doktor.
- Kdo z vs je pbuznm Miny Kao?

528
01:00:14,520 --> 01:00:16,715
J. Jak je j?

529
01:00:16,840 --> 01:00:20,150
Je v kritickm stavu
a potebuje operaci.

530
01:00:20,280 --> 01:00:21,998
Je ale thotn.

531
01:00:22,120 --> 01:00:26,352
Podn anestetik by mohlo
tomu dtti ukodit.

532
01:00:26,480 --> 01:00:30,917
Bez anestezie ovem bude mra
spnosti operace polovin.

533
01:00:31,040 --> 01:00:34,396
Postarejte se, prosm, hlavn o ni.
A to stoj, co chce.

534
01:00:35,520 --> 01:00:38,557
J tu bolest vydrm. Pomozte mi,
prosm, udret naivu to dt.

535
01:01:29,200 --> 01:01:32,510
Policie m pkaz k naemu zaten.

536
01:01:32,640 --> 01:01:35,473
Zastraovn nm nijak nepome.

537
01:01:35,600 --> 01:01:39,388
Brate, prosm, poslouchej mn.
Mli bychom se na chvli ukrt.

538
01:01:39,520 --> 01:01:41,715
Pod se meme vrtit nkdy jindy.

539
01:01:41,840 --> 01:01:47,437
Mluvila jsem se stkem Gouem.
Popluje lod do Panamy.

540
01:01:58,520 --> 01:02:01,990
Ahoj, Mino, jak je? U lp?

541
01:02:06,320 --> 01:02:08,470
Mohlo by to bt nakaliv.

542
01:02:08,600 --> 01:02:12,752
- Mina nen nakaliv ani tak.
- Obvm se, e byste mohl nakazit vy ji.

543
01:02:12,880 --> 01:02:17,829
Kdo v, jestli nemte njak
pohlavn penosn choroby? Potebuju rat.

544
01:02:29,480 --> 01:02:33,075
Mrtv z hrobu nevstanou.
Netruchlete a pli.

545
01:02:33,200 --> 01:02:35,953
- Moc dkuji.
- Nen teba bt formln.

546
01:02:36,080 --> 01:02:41,757
, ano, f se rozhodl vs odmnit
medail nazvanou "Hrd rodina policist".

547
01:02:42,360 --> 01:02:45,716
Mj jedin syn je mrtv.

548
01:02:45,840 --> 01:02:49,150
Ta medaile pro mn nic neznamen.

549
01:02:49,280 --> 01:02:52,989
Nkte lid umraj zbyten
a nkte ne.

550
01:02:53,120 --> 01:02:56,317
Mla byste bt hrd.

551
01:02:58,000 --> 01:03:00,639
Dvejte si, prosm, pozor na pusu.

552
01:03:00,760 --> 01:03:05,880
Mte opravdov tst, matko.
Pod jet mte tohohle vnuka.

553
01:03:07,240 --> 01:03:08,389
Pane Lau.

554
01:03:08,520 --> 01:03:14,311
Jen odpovej, Mino. Jet jsi
se neuzdravila. Dej si na as.

555
01:03:14,440 --> 01:03:17,716
O ten vietnamsk ppad
nemus mt starost.

556
01:03:17,840 --> 01:03:20,673
Matko, Hungu,
pane Lau.

557
01:03:20,800 --> 01:03:25,157
Kdy u tu jste vichni
mu vm ct i tohle.

558
01:03:25,280 --> 01:03:29,159
Uzavel jsem to
a vy si berete msc dovolen.

559
01:03:29,640 --> 01:03:33,269
- My si te volno vzt nememe.
- Pokud ne te, tak kdy?

560
01:03:33,400 --> 01:03:37,439
- Nemli bychom ekat na dal velk den?
- O jakm velkm dnu to mluvte?

561
01:03:37,560 --> 01:03:42,953
Vm, e jste vichni neastn.
Nezapomete respektovat svho nadzenho.

562
01:03:43,080 --> 01:03:45,719
N bratr kvli tomuhle ppadu zemel.

563
01:03:45,840 --> 01:03:48,798
- Pokejte s tou dovolenou, prosm.
- Ticho!

564
01:03:48,920 --> 01:03:51,992
Vy nejste policejn komisa.
O tomhle rozhodnout nemete.

565
01:03:52,120 --> 01:03:57,592
Tenhle ppad mm te
na starosti j, vrchn inspektore.

566
01:03:57,720 --> 01:04:01,872
Pokud vm eknu, e si mte dat pauzu,
nikdo vm nesm ct opak.

567
01:04:02,560 --> 01:04:08,157
Pane Lau, kdy byl jejich otec naivu,
tak na vs dval pozor.

568
01:04:08,280 --> 01:04:13,434
Nechte je ten ppad vyeit
jet, ne pjdou na dovolenou,

569
01:04:14,560 --> 01:04:20,271
aby mrtv mohli odpovat v pokoji
a ti, je ij, mohli bt spokojeni.

570
01:04:20,400 --> 01:04:22,834
J bych si to i rozmyslel.

571
01:04:22,960 --> 01:04:26,555
Jene z toho, co jem prv slyel,
se zd, e se chtj pomstt.

572
01:04:26,680 --> 01:04:30,036
Upmn, v takovmhle rozpoloen
moc uiten nebudou.

573
01:04:30,160 --> 01:04:34,836
Budou snadno dlat chyby.
Mohly by vechny skonit mrtv.

574
01:04:34,960 --> 01:04:36,996
Mrtvej budete vy, ne my!

575
01:04:37,120 --> 01:04:39,759
Pokoute se mn napadnout?

576
01:04:39,880 --> 01:04:43,509
Pokud se mn, svho nadzenho,
pokuste napadnout, vzdte se kariry.

577
01:04:43,640 --> 01:04:47,633
- Mj kmotr vm v minulosti pomohl.
- Nemluvte o starch asech.

578
01:04:47,760 --> 01:04:52,959
Je r. 1990. Mm nadzenm jste byl,
ale te mme hodnost stejnou.

579
01:04:53,080 --> 01:04:55,548
Ty hajzle.
Potebuje podnou nakldaku!

580
01:04:55,680 --> 01:04:58,513
Nedlejte to.
Jste vy policejn dstojnk.

581
01:04:58,640 --> 01:05:02,952
Pokud pjdete proti zkonu,
pijdete o prci.

582
01:05:05,720 --> 01:05:10,077
J jsem jen ena v domcnosti.
Mn za napaden policisty nahlsit mete.

583
01:05:10,200 --> 01:05:14,478
- Ho, vyprovo nvtvu.
- Prosm, odejdte, pane Lau.

584
01:05:14,600 --> 01:05:19,037
Nemuste mn vyprovzet.
J rozumm.

585
01:05:19,160 --> 01:05:22,994
Kdybych byl ve va ki,
reagoval bych stejn.

586
01:05:24,560 --> 01:05:26,835
Podn si odpoi, Mino.

587
01:05:31,640 --> 01:05:33,676
Mu st uvit,
e mn suspendovali, matko.

588
01:05:33,800 --> 01:05:36,109
Nebylo to vi tob spravedliv.

589
01:05:37,240 --> 01:05:39,515
Te m ten ppad na starosti Lau.

590
01:05:39,640 --> 01:05:42,871
- Nemj strach. Nco vymyslme.
- Podle tch zprv

591
01:05:43,000 --> 01:05:46,037
m ten gang v plnu
opustit Hong Kong.

592
01:05:46,160 --> 01:05:48,549
Musme je vechny chytit.

593
01:06:12,040 --> 01:06:17,956
Ty informace odhaluj, e odplouvaj
ztra rno v 6 z pstavu Tsun Mun.

594
01:06:18,080 --> 01:06:21,675
Musme nae tmy zorganizovat tak,
aby je chytili brzy rno.

595
01:06:21,800 --> 01:06:26,555
Musme zajistit utajen.
Nikdo nesm nic prozradit.

596
01:06:32,440 --> 01:06:35,000
- Mohl by jsi pijt o prci.
- Nemj strach.

597
01:06:35,120 --> 01:06:39,591
Jsme jako brati.
Te se vrtm zptky do kancele.

598
01:06:39,720 --> 01:06:43,156
Musm odejt nco zadit, matko.

599
01:06:43,280 --> 01:06:47,592
Ti Vietnamci odplouvaj lod
ztra rno v 6 z pstavu Tsun Mun.

600
01:06:47,720 --> 01:06:50,473
Tuhle pleitost nesmme propsnout.

601
01:06:50,600 --> 01:06:54,036
Musme se tam dostat dv
ne Lau a chytit je.

602
01:06:55,040 --> 01:06:58,510
Dobe, uvidme se v 5 rno na molu.

603
01:07:35,760 --> 01:07:39,389
Nechci, aby tv rodina
kvli mn trpla, Chung Bo

604
01:07:39,520 --> 01:07:42,512
Poehnej mi, prosm, z nebe.

605
01:09:11,400 --> 01:09:14,119
Jsou na lodi.

606
01:09:23,080 --> 01:09:25,640
Lodnku, sledujte, prosm tu lo.

607
01:09:25,760 --> 01:09:27,557
Dobr.

608
01:09:27,680 --> 01:09:33,516
Odplout ve tyi msto v est
bylo nhl rozhodnut.

609
01:09:33,640 --> 01:09:37,679
Kdy jsme posledn opoutli Vietnam,
byl jsi to ty, kdo zajioval pepravu.

610
01:09:37,800 --> 01:09:39,916
kal jsi mi, e ta lo
odplouv v 6 rno.

611
01:09:40,040 --> 01:09:44,716
Byl jsem rd, e jsem dorazil ve 4,
jinak bych jet pod byl v lgru.

612
01:09:44,840 --> 01:09:46,796
- Je ten pevoznk spolehliv?
- Nemj strach.

613
01:09:46,920 --> 01:09:50,595
Jeho lo je pln neleglnho zbo.
Neme si dovolit ns podvst.

614
01:09:50,720 --> 01:09:52,756
eknte posdce,
a hned pestane pracovat.

615
01:09:52,880 --> 01:09:54,757
- Bte.
- Ano.

616
01:10:00,120 --> 01:10:04,796
Tohle jsou ti lid, kapitne.
Wah, tohle je kapitn.

617
01:10:04,920 --> 01:10:07,912
- Dkuji a omlouvm se.
- Pojte se mnou.

618
01:10:16,640 --> 01:10:18,790
Pojte tudy.

619
01:10:21,400 --> 01:10:23,595
Kapitne.

620
01:10:24,800 --> 01:10:30,557
Prozatm zstate tady. A budeme
v mezinrodnch vodch, mete ven.

621
01:10:34,920 --> 01:10:37,718
Vezmi si tuhle pistoli, Wah.

622
01:10:37,840 --> 01:10:43,551
Jen pro jistotu. Jakmile se dostane
do mezinrodnch vod, bude v bezpe.

623
01:10:44,280 --> 01:10:47,636
Bu opatrn, mj drah brate.

624
01:10:47,760 --> 01:10:49,910
J te pjdu.

625
01:11:01,120 --> 01:11:03,509
- Doplujte prosm ke behu, lodnku.
- Jist.

626
01:11:17,040 --> 01:11:18,189
Jdem.

627
01:12:19,960 --> 01:12:21,313
Auto Ling.

628
01:12:29,240 --> 01:12:33,074
- Pijela sem njak dvka?
- Na tu lo se nalodily dvky dv.

629
01:13:25,640 --> 01:13:28,916
- Co se to stalo?
- Zstate dole!

630
01:13:32,400 --> 01:13:34,356
Zastelte ji!

631
01:13:38,160 --> 01:13:40,037
Kapitne, zavolejte pomoc.

632
01:13:50,400 --> 01:13:52,197
Zptky.

633
01:13:54,880 --> 01:13:56,996
Pojte. Jdeme.

634
01:16:44,560 --> 01:16:46,516
Zastav.

635
01:18:38,400 --> 01:18:40,994
Zstate stt!

636
01:18:41,120 --> 01:18:43,429
Zahote to!

637
01:18:43,560 --> 01:18:45,391
Tam!

638
01:18:45,520 --> 01:18:47,476
Dlej!

639
01:19:12,880 --> 01:19:16,429
Mino, nezabjej ho.
Tohle neobhj.

640
01:19:20,880 --> 01:19:23,235
Neudlej nic hloupho.

641
01:19:41,040 --> 01:19:43,634
Vyla jste si zabhat, matko?

642
01:19:43,760 --> 01:19:46,672
Bute pesto opatrn.
Tady nejsme ve starobinci.

643
01:19:46,800 --> 01:19:48,950
Na ulicch je spousta padouch.

644
01:19:49,080 --> 01:19:51,753
V takhle tenkm obleen
byste se mohla nachladit.

645
01:19:51,880 --> 01:19:58,149
Nachlazen mi nevad.Chci jen
vidt ty padouchy zaten.

646
01:19:58,280 --> 01:20:00,316
Nechte na policii, a to zad.

647
01:20:00,440 --> 01:20:04,752
Vy u jste na pomoc star.

648
01:20:05,680 --> 01:20:08,353
Vrchn inspektor Hung
toho chlapa zatkl.

649
01:20:12,440 --> 01:20:15,637
A pak kdo je neuitenej.

650
01:20:26,000 --> 01:20:29,436
Vrchn inspektore Hungu,
poruil jste nelnkv rozkaz.

651
01:20:29,560 --> 01:20:34,190
Nyn vs, z moci vyho dstojnka, zatkm.

652
01:20:34,320 --> 01:20:36,629
- Nasate mu pouta.
- Ano, pane.

653
01:20:52,000 --> 01:20:54,116
Nepibliujte se ke mn,
jinak ji zabiju!

654
01:20:54,760 --> 01:20:58,309
- Nen teba.
- Ani hnout, jinak zeme se mnou!

655
01:20:58,440 --> 01:21:00,476
Dobe.

656
01:21:00,600 --> 01:21:04,229
Pak tedy zeme s tebou.

657
01:21:04,360 --> 01:21:07,272
Seberte ho!

658
01:21:08,920 --> 01:21:11,150
A ustoup!

659
01:21:11,280 --> 01:21:12,793
Ustupte.

660
01:21:14,480 --> 01:21:17,119
Pokud se ke m piblte, zabiju ji!

661
01:21:17,240 --> 01:21:20,232
Klidn ji zabij.
Syna u jsi mi zabil.

662
01:21:20,360 --> 01:21:25,070
Pokud ume i tahle dcera, o moc vc
mi to neubl. No, tak ji zab, hajzle.

663
01:21:25,200 --> 01:21:27,316
Pokud t zabiju, budu mt kld.

664
01:21:27,440 --> 01:21:30,273
No, tak. Nem na to?
Zab ji.

665
01:21:30,400 --> 01:21:32,595
- Dlej.
- Stjte!

666
01:21:48,200 --> 01:21:50,873
Jet ne.

667
01:21:53,160 --> 01:21:54,912
Te!

668
01:21:58,320 --> 01:22:02,552
Budu v podku. Neplate.

669
01:24:06,200 --> 01:24:12,036
Ty jsi mi zabila bratra.
Te za jeho smrt zaplat.

670
01:24:13,200 --> 01:24:18,672
Jedna z ns mus zemt.
Te uvid, co dovedu.

671
01:25:28,840 --> 01:25:31,035
Vstvej. No, tak vstvej.

672
01:25:34,120 --> 01:25:36,315
No tak. No tak.

673
01:25:40,680 --> 01:25:43,353
No tak. Pra m.

674
01:25:47,920 --> 01:25:50,354
Te zeme.

675
